name: Glory  - Artwork from the comic by DoctorWu

metadata.name: Glory  - Celebration in the Grand Ballroom
metadata.description: " Glory " is the main character of my comic I am presently working on. She is a half demon and half human living in our present day world. Glory is 20 years old and just trying to fit in. She puts up with a lot of bullying and name calling. Presently she as some smaller super powers, but soon will be getting some huge powers. The sales of these NFTS will go towards funds to print the comic and later release it as a PDF - NFT
